WebIndex : like WebSiteView with relative paths. Directories consecutive.
USE THIS FOR THE BLOG-STYLE SITE.

SiteView: like WebSiteView with absolute paths. Directory table.

WebSiteView: for relative references. Works: give full directory paths.
             Directory table.

SiteIndex: like WebSiteView with absolute paths. Directories listed
           consecutively.

WebView: like WebSiteView with dates. Directory table.
